    <p>With an RTP rate of 96.0%, you might be wondering what else this game has in store. Well, for one thing, it has an awesome disco-themed soundtrack that will make you want to put on your dancing shoes. And the golden glitter graphics will have you feeling like you're in a fancy casino in Las Vegas, minus the overpriced drinks.</p>"
